<emphasis box="[258,417,2071,2091]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="350">Microvelia nelsoni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, female. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[499,520,2071,2091]" pageId="1" pageNumber="350">A.</emphasis>
Dorsal view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[640,659,2071,2091]" pageId="1" pageNumber="350">B.</emphasis>
